short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quick Launcher for Steemit blockchain and Bittrex exchange.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Steemit Quick Launcher extension provides a quick and easy way to access your Steemit blockchain accounts. 

You can quickly and easily launch the blockchain below and speedily manage your accounts.

*Steemit
*DTube
*Catchawhale
*Voting worth
*BlockTrades
*Bittrex
*Steem Tools
*Steemit Help
